		<title>Windows でも Grep したい - remark</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://text.baldanders.info/remark/2018/03/grep/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2018-03-07:/remark/2018/03/grep/</id>
